&lt;li&gt;Label incoming parts and components accurately to maintain full traceability across the facility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move verified inventory to its correct storage location or production stage without delay.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspect incoming items for transit damage and escalate findings to management promptly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organize and complete all paperwork for accurate digital filing and data entry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean, safe, and well-organized loading dock to reduce risk and keep operations efficient.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
